content:
Dan Reynolds did something on December 4th that he only does once a year, get older :-)

I was thinking he didn’t say anything about it because he was afraid we would give him [something like this for this](http://web.archive.org/web/20060103050924/http:/www.halloweencostumes4u.com/Merchant2/merchant.mvc?store_code=hal&screen=PROD&product_code=rub50680)  
 for his birthday :-)
